20former%20president%20said%20at%20an%20agricultural%20policy%20roundtable%20in%20Smithton%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20that%20he%20would%20impose%20the%20massive%20tariff%20if%20John%20Deere%20follows%20through%20on%20its%20plans%20to%20move%20some%20of%20its%20production%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%2C%20skid%20steer%20loaders%20and%20compact%20track%20loaders%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Iowa%20to%20Mexico%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20first%20announced%20the%20partial%20production%20shift%20to%20Mexico%20back%20in%20June%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Feconomy%2Fjohn-deere-announces-mass-layoffs-midwest-amid-production-shift-mexico%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Fox%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fdeere-layoffs-2024-what-to-know-about-the-latest-job-cuts-1033454578%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efollowing%20several%20rounds%20of%20staff%20cuts.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20a%20lot%20about%20John%20Deere.%20I%20love%20the%20company%2C%20but%20as%20you%20know%2C%20they've%20announced%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20move%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20manufacturing%20business%20to%20Mexico%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20at%20Monday's%20event.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20notifying%20John%20Deere%20right%20now%3A%20If%20you%20do%20that%2C%20we're%20putting%20a%20200%25%20tariff%20on%20everything%20that%20you%20want%20to%20sell%20into%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20think%20they're%20going%20to%20make%20product%20cheaper%20in%20Mexico%20and%20then%20sell%20it%20in%20for%20the%20same%20price%20as%20they%20did%20before%2C%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20by%20getting%20rid%20of%20our%20labor%20and%20our%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20nominee%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20said%20that%20any%20company%20that%20did%20the%20same%20would%20be%20slapped%20with%20the%20same%20200%25%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Deere%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20W.%20Coppess%2C%20director%20of%20agriculture%20policy%20program%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Urbana-Champaign%2C%20said%20that%20Trump%20is%20tapping%20into%20concerns%20about%20companies%20moving%20jobs%20out%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20a%20pattern%20we've%20seen%20many%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJohn%20Deere%20is%20a%20major%20manufacturer%20and%20the%20consequences%20of%20moving%20those%20jobs%20is%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20Coppess%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Coppess%20said%20Trump's%20answer%20to%20the%20problem%20might%20not%20be%20the%20right%20fix%20%E2%80%94%20and%20several%20trade%20economists%20told%20BI%20that%20Trump's%20proposed%20tariff%20is%20a%20terrible%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20find%20no%20serious%2C%20respected%20trade%20economists%20thinking%20that%20this%20is%20a%20good%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20Ian%20Sheldon%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20Andersons%20Chair%20of%20Agricultural%20Marketing%2C%20Trade%20and%20Policy%20at%20The%20Ohio%20State%20University%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20huge%20tariff%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheldon%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20almost%20like%20a%20prohibitive%20tariff.%20By%20prohibitive%2C%20I%20mean%20it%20would%20choke%20off%20imports%20of%20John%20Deere%20skid%20steer%20loaders%20would%20be%20my%20hunch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGary%20Hufbauer%2C%20a%20nonresident%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Peterson%20Institute%20for%20International%20Economics%2C%20echoed%20Sheldon's%20concerns.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20that%20Trump's%20huge%20proposed%20tariff%20is%20not%20only%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20would%20also%20violate%20the%20United%20States-Mexico-Canada%20Agreement%20(USMCA)%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fustr.gov%2Ftrade-agreements%2Ffree-trade-agreements%2Funited-states-mexico-canada-agreement%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520United%2520States%252DMexico%252DCanada%2520Agreement%2520(USMCA)%2520entered%2Cfarmers%252C%2520ranchers%252C%2520and%2520businesses.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esucceeded%20NAFTA%20in%202020%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20plain%2C%20simple%20violation%2C%26quot%3B%20Hufbauer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222425%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22line%20of%20green%20john%20deere%20tractors%20in%20a%20dirt%20lot%20with%20snow%20capped%20mountains%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a5eddc43bb77284b9d2db5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Deere%20is%20the%20latest%20company%20to%20face%20a%20threat%20of%20tariffs%20from%20Donald%20Trump.%3Cp%3ERick%20Wilking%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESheldon%20said%20he's%20also%20not%20convinced%20Trump's%20threatened%20tariffs%20would%20even%20be%20feasible%20under%20USMCA.%20He%20expects%20that%20Mexico%20would%20immediately%20file%20a%20dispute%20with%20the%20USMCA%20dispute%20resolution%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20could%20lead%20Mexico%20to%20retaliate%20against%20the%20US%2C%20Sheldon%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20this%20integrated%20market%20in%20North%20America%2C%20and%20we're%20already%20in%20a%20trade%20dispute%20with%20Mexico%20over%20genetically%20modified%20corn%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheldon%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20counterproductive%20to%20me%20to%20potentially%20exacerbate%20trade%20relations%20with%20one%20of%20our%20large%20trading%20partners.%20It%20doesn't%20make%20any%20sense%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHufbauer%20also%20cautioned%20that%20such%20a%20tariff%2C%20if%20it%20were%20to%20be%20imposed%2C%20would%20weaken%20US-Mexico%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20immediate%20effect%20would%20be%20very%20hostile%20relations%20with%20Mexico%2C%26quot%3B%20Hufbauer%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fusafacts.org%2Farticles%2Fwho-are-the-uss-top-trade-partners%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOver%252050%2525%2520of%25202023%2520US%2CChina%252C%2520Germany%252C%2520and%2520Japan.%26amp%3Btext%3DHome%2520%2F%2520Economy%2520%2F%2520Articles%2520%2F%2520Who%2Call%2520US%2520trade%2520in%25202023.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMexico%20as%20the%20US's%20biggest%20trading%20partner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20US%20would%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20lose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20get%20a%20higher%20cost%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20products%20in%20the%20US%20that%20we%20are%20now%20accustomed%20to%20having%20from%20Mexico%2C%26quot%3B%20Hufbauer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20costly%20for%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BBut%20beyond%20that%2C%20if%20we%20get%20into%20a%20hostile%20trading%20relation%20with%20Mexico%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20reverberate%20down%20into%20Central%20America%20and%20South%20America%20for%20sure.%20It'll%20start%20with%20Mexico%2C%20and%20you're%20just%20going%20to%20get%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20Western%20Hemisphere%20feeling%20pretty%20hostile%20about%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20say%20it%20could%20also%20cost%20American%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20Bivens%20Collinson%2C%20managing%20principal%20at%20international%20trade%20law%20and%20policy%20law%20firm%20Sandler%2C%20Travis%20%26amp%3B%20Rosenberg%2C%20said%20that%20any%20tariffs%20applied%20to%20products%20are%20ultimately%20paid%20by%20the%20consumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoppess%20said%20there%20would%20also%20be%20concerns%20about%20equipment%20availability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-threat-cut-gms-electric-car-subsidies-meaningless-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20has%20threatened%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Trump's%20threat%20to%20impose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-warns-that-companies-leaving-the-us-will-face-retribution-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20tariffs%20on%20imports%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20isn't%20new.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20a%20pillar%20of%20his%20economic%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-plan-inflation-policy-impact-trade-war-china-rates-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20has%20already%20vowed%20to%20implement%20a%2010%25%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20all%20imports%20in%20the%20US%20and%20a%2060%25%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20imports.%20The%20former%20president%20also%20called%20for%20100%25%20tariffs%20on%20cars%20produced%20in%20Mexico%20at%20a%20speech%20in%20Georgia%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20candidate's%20goal%20is%20to%20bring%20production%20back%20to%20the%20US%2C%20but%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-plan-inflation-policy-impact-trade-war-china-rates-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomists%20have%20said%20the%20plan%20could%20increase%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20word%20tariff%20properly%20used%20is%20a%20beautiful%20word%E2%80%A6A%20lot%20of%20bad%20people%20didn't%20like%20that%20word%2C%20but%20now%20they're%20finding%20out%20I%20was%20right%2C%20and%20we%20will%20take%20in%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20our%20treasury%20and%20use%20that%20money%20to%20benefit%20the%20American%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20will%20not%20cause%20inflation%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20tariff%20goals%20going%20into%20the%20next%20election%20go%20beyond%20his%20