quot%3BIf%20someone%20like%20Kamla%20can%20lose%20everything%2C%20what%20chance%20do%20others%20have%3F%26quot%3B%20Himanshi%20asked%20herself%20then.%20Kamla%20had%20returned%20from%20Delhi%20to%20her%20village%2C%20Achrol%2C%20in%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0This%20question%20inspired%20Himanshi%20to%20build%20Bare%20Craft%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20uses%20AI%20as%20a%20tool%20and%20a%20lifeline%20for%20artisans%20like%20Kamla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%205%2C500%20verified%20artisans%20are%20on%20the%20Bare%20Craft%20platform%2C%20each%20rooted%20in%20traditional%20crafts%20like%20block%20printing%2C%20Chikankari%20embroidery%2C%20and%20Kantha%20work.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20solve%20problems%20like%20transparency%20in%20supply%20chains%2C%20fair%20wages%2C%20and%20sustainable%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20Himanshi%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform's%20AI%20matches%20the%20right%20artisans%20with%20suitable%20projects%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20(SMEs)%20to%20source%20high-quality%20crafts.%20Himanshi%2C%20the%20founding%20member%2C%20works%20pro%20bono%20to%20support%20the%20platform's%20growth%20and%20market%20connections%2C%20while%20her%20mother%2C%20Kiran%20Singh%2C%20oversees%20its%20operations%20with%20the%20artisan%20communities.%20This%20arrangement%20allows%20Himanshi%20to%20continue%20her%20professional%20work%20with%20other%20nonprofits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Meets%20Artisans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20artisan%20is%20Monu%20Saini%2C%20a%20block%20printing%20artisan%20based%20near%20Achrol%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20who%20has%20dedicated%20over%20a%20decade%20to%20his%20craft.%20Through%20the%20Bare%20Craft%20initiative%2C%20Monu%20refined%20his%20skills%20and%20trained%2025%20women%20in%20block%20printing%2C%20empowering%20them%20to%20pursue%20financial%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHand%20block%20printing%20doesn't%20involve%20any%20chemicals%20and%20is%20good%20for%20the%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Monu%20says.%20His%20passion%20for%20sustainability%20and%20community-building%20has%20allowed%20him%20to%20collaborate%20with%20international%20designers.%20Recently%2C%20he%20began%20working%20with%20US-based%20designers%20to%20blend%20traditional%20techniques%20with%20modern%20designs.%20%26quot%3BThrough%20Bare%20Craft%2C%20I've%20connected%20with%20small%20retailers%20and%20individual%20buyers%2C%26quot%3B%20Monu%20says.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20helped%20me%20broaden%20the%20reach%20of%20my%20creations%20while%20preserving%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20block%20printing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBare%20Craft's%20AI%20system%20has%20shown%20impressive%20results.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20a%2010%25%20increase%20in%20revenue%20for%20artisans%20and%20SMEs%2C%20with%20a%2050%25%20reduction%20in%20production%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Himanshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20might%20seem%20an%20unlikely%20ally%20for%20traditional%20artisans%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20engine%20driving%20Bare%20Craft.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20a%20catalogue%2C%26quot%3B%20Himanshi%20says.%20%26quot%3BAI%20helps%20us%20recommend%20raw%20materials%2C%20cuts%20down%20on%20production%20time%2C%20and%20ensures%20that%20artisans%20get%20paid%20fairly%2C%20all%20while%20minimising%20costs%20for%20buyers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20platform's%20first%20successes%20was%20a%20designer%20dress%20that%20combined%20block%20printing%2C%20chikankari%20embroidery%2C%20and%20kantha%20work%20-%20three%20distinct%20crafts%2C%20each%20completed%20by%20artisans%20in%20different%20cities.%20The%20final%20product%20directly%20supported%20six%20artisans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20empowered%20over%20150%20artisans%20with%20training%2C%20helping%20them%20adapt%20to%20a%20changing%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Himanshi%20says.%20Additionally%2C%2082%25%20of%20the%20artisans%20on%20the%20platform%20have%20successfully%20connected%20to%20new%20markets%2C%20and%2023%20have%20launched%20independent%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20fashion.%20Bare%20Craft%20is%20helping%20artisans%20turn%20waste%20into%20treasure%2C%20like%20converting%20hosiery%20waste%20into%20cotton%20stationery%2C%20a%20completely%20sustainable%20solution.%20An%20example%20is%20when%20an%20SME%20buyer%20started%20looking%20at%20textile%20waste%20as%20a%20raw%20material%20to%20produce%20their%20products%20-%20an%20option%20not%20easily%20available%20earlier.%20The%20system%20removed%20the%20pressure%20of%20visiting%20different%20sites%2C%20sorting%20the%20waste%2C%20and%20making%20it%20ready%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EScaling%20Art%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBare%20Craft%20plans%20to%20scale%20its%20artisan%20training%20program%20to%20reach%201%2C00%2C000%20artisans%20and%20achieve%20a%2099%25%20market%20linkage%20rate.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20also%20expanding%20to%20connect%20100%20SMEs%20with%20artisans%20to%20create%20more%20collaborations%20that%20benefit%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Himanshi%20says.%20Her%C2%A0AI%20application%20also%20optimises%20raw%20material%20selection%20and%20streamlines%20logistics%2C%20ensuring%20that%20every%20step%20of%20the%20process%2C%20from%20production%20to%20delivery%2C%20is%20smooth%20and%20cost-effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Bare%20Craft%20plans%20to%20introduce%20digital%20passports%20for%20products.%20This%20will%20help%20buyers%20see%20the%20entire%20journey%20of%20their%20purchase%2C%20from%20raw%20material%20to%20finished%20product.%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20just%20about%20selling%20crafts%2C%20it's%20about%20making%20people%20understand%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20purchase%2C%26quot%3B%20Himanshi%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20AI%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3