%20that%20they%20are%20the%20only%20two%20countries%20with%20over%20a%20billion%20people%2C%20both%20rising%20in%20the%20global%20order%20and%20who%20often%20have%20overlapping%20peripheries%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20a%20common%20border.%20So%20it's%20really%20a%20very%20complicated%20issue.%20I%20think%2C%20if%20you%20look%20today%20in%20global%20politics%2C%20the%20parallel%20rises%20of%20India%20and%20China%20present%20a%20very%2C%20very%20unique%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20referred%20to%20a%20recent%20remark%20that%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20disengagement%20problems%20with%20China%20have%20been%20sorted%20out.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20said%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20it%20has%20been%20sorted%20out%20-%20I%20was%20asked%20in%20a%20way%20to%20quantify%20-%20it's%20only%20of%20the%20disengagement.%20So%20that's%20one%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%20The%20main%20issue%20right%20now%20is%20the%20patrolling.%20You%20know%2C%20how%20do%20we%2C%20both%20of%20us%2C%20patrol%20up%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jaishankar%20said%20patrolling%20arrangements%20have%20been%20disturbed%20after%202020.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20sort%20out%20much%20of%20the%20disengagement%2C%20the%20friction%20points%2C%20but%20some%20of%20the%20patrolling%20issues%20need%20to%20be%20resolved.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20once%20the%20disengagement%20issue%20is%20dealt%20with%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20the%20larger%20issue%20as%20both%20of%20us%20have%20brought%20a%20very%20large%20number%20of%20troops%20up%20to%20the%20border%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20is%20what%20we%20call%20the%20de-escalation%20issue%2C%20and%20then%20there%20is%20the%20larger%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20really%2C%20how%20do%20you%20deal%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20relationship%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bentire%203500%20kilometre-border%20between%20India%20and%20China%20is%20disputed%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20you%20make%20sure%20the%20border%20is%20peaceful%20so%20that%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20relationship%20can%20move.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jaishankar%20said%20several%20agreements%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20detailed%20how%20to%20ensure%20the%20border%20remained%20peaceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20the%20problem%20was%20in%202020%2C%20despite%20these%20very%20explicit%20agreements%2C%20we%20saw%20that%20the%20Chinese%20-%20we%20were%20all%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Covid%20at%20that%20time%20-%20moved%20a%20large%20number%20of%20forces%20in%20violation%20of%20these%20agreements%20to%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%20And%20we%20responded%20in%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20troops%20were%20deployed%20very%20close%20up%2C%20which%20is%20'very%20dangerous'%2C%20it%20was%20likely%20a%20mishap%20could%20happen%2C%20and%20it%20did%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%202020%20Galwan%20clash%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20there%20was%20a%20clash%2C%20and%20a%20number%20of%20troops%20died%20on%20either%20side%2C%20and%20that%20has%20since%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20overshadowed%20the%20relationship.%20So%20until%20we%20can%20restore%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20on%20the%20border%20and%20ensure%20the%20agreements%20signed%20up%20to%20are%20adhered%20to%2C%20it's%20obviously%20difficult%20to%20carry%20on%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20said%20the%20focus%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20had%20been%20to%20at%20least%20disengage%20the%20troops%2C%20meaning%20that%20they%20go%20back%20to%20the%20camp%2C%20the%20military%20bases%20from%20which%20they%20traditionally%20operate.%C2%A0%26quot%3BBecause%20right%20now%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20troops%20deployed%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A172724340