%2C%20People's%20Bank%20of%20China%2C%20or%20POBC%2C%20governor%20Pan%20Gongsheng%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Flianbo%2Ffabu%2F202409%2Fcontent_6976186.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20cuts%20to%20several%20interest%20rates%20and%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20banks%20need%20to%20hold%20in%20reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PBOC%20unleashed%20policy%20euphoria%20as%20markets%20deemed%20the%20'big%20guns'%20unleashed%20with%20the%20rash%20of%20aggressive%20stimulus%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishnu%20Varathan%2C%20Mizuho's%20macro%20research%20head%20for%20Asia%20excluding%20Japan%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20not%20only%20boosted%20China's%20previously%20downbeat%20stock%20markets%2C%20but%20also%20helped%20the%20yuan%20pull%20off%20a%20%26quot%3Bremarkable%20surge%2C%26quot%3B%20Varathan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20US%20dollar%20to%20offshore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fusd-cnh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20yuan%2C%20or%20CNH%3C%2Fa%3E%20rate%20fell%20to%20as%20low%20as%206.9951%2C%20the%20first%20time%20it%20breached%20the%207%20per%20dollar%20level%20since%20May%202023.%20This%20means%20%241%20could%20buy%20fewer%20Chinese%20yuan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20USD%2FCNH%20is%20about%201.6%25%20lower%20so%20far%20this%20year.%20The%20currency%20pair%20was%20now%20around%20the%207.01%20level%20at%2012%20p.m.%20in%20China%20Standard%20Time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20yuan%20has%20been%20strengthening%20recently%2C%20and%20this%20trend%20is%20not%20all%20thanks%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserve-interest-rate-cuts-mortgage-investment-credit-savings-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Federal%20Reserve%20%3C%2Fa%3Eannounced%20a%20big%20interest%20rate%20cut%20last%20week.%20This%20is%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20because%20rate%20cuts%20mean%20yields%20in%20dollar%20assets%20would%20be%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20anticipation%20of%20the%20Fed%20rate%20cut%2C%20the%20yuan%20has%20been%20strengthening%20against%20the%20dollar%20since%20end-June%2C%20in%20part%20because%20some%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-china-businesses-hoarding-us-dollars-fx-earnings-yuan-renminbi-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20exporters%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20been%20repatriating%20dollar%20earnings%20they%20were%20hoarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20capital%20inflows%20into%20China%20reached%20%247%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20inflow%20since%20July%202023%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20from%20Larry%20Hu%2C%20the%20head%20of%20China%20economics%20at%20Macquarie%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExporters%20also%20converted%20%2437%20billion%20of%20foreign%20exchange%20into%20the%20yuan%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20level%20since%20September%202022%2C%20Hu%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228225dc60-2f22-4782-b4cc-9e3fef15b93f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20strong%20yuan%20is%20bad%20for%20exports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20a%20strong%20yuan%20signals%20confidence%20in%20China's%20economy%2C%20analysts%20aren't%20sure%20the%20gains%20will%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20a%20stronger%20yuan%20would%20make%20China's%20exports%20more%20expensive%20and%20less%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20China's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-household-deposits-savings-luxury-consumer-demand-slowdown-economy-outlook-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20confidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20really%20weak%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-weak-domestic-demand-factory-activity-amid-strong-export-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edomestic%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20flagging%2C%20while%20exports%20%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20pillar%20of%20the%20country's%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20robust%2C%20Beijing%20may%20not%20be%20happy%20keeping%20the%20yuan%20stronger%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Swiss%20private%20bank%20Lombard%20Odier's%20CIO%20office%20wrote%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%20inconsistency%26quot%3B%20between%20a%20strong%20yuan%20and%20credible%20reflation%2C%20which%20refers%20to%20policies%20intended%20to%20reverse%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-markets-deflation-chart-investors-consumer-prices-outlook-beijing-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20economic%20challenge%20China%20is%20facing%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20a%20tight%20grip%20on%20the%20yuan%2C%20so%20Beijing%20does%20have%20a%20big%20influence%20on%20the%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Pan%20said%20China%20will%20prevent%20the%20markets%20from%20forming%20one-sided%20expectations%20and%20guard%20against%20the%20risk%20of%20the%20yuan%20overshooting%20so%20that%20the%20currency's%20exchange%20rate%20can%20be%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20and%20balanced%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbc.gov.cn%2Fzhengcehuobisi%2F125207%2F125217%2F125925%2F5467164%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20central%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicated%20its%20neutral%20stance%20on%20the%20yuan%20via%20way%20of%20its%20daily%20midpoint%20fix%2C%20which%20it%20pegged%20at%207.0202%20per%20dollar%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20against%20the%207.0206%20traders%20and%20analysts%20had%20estimated%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-09-25%2Fyuan-rallies-past-7-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20survey.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20yuan%20is%20allowed%20to%20trade%20within%20a%202%25%20range%20above%20or%20below%20the%20midpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacquarie's%20Hu%20wrote%20in%20his%20note%20on%20Friday%20that%20there%20may%20limited%20room%20for%20the%20yuan%20to%20gain%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20falling%20US%20yield%20may%20encourage%20exporters%20to%20convert%20more%20dollars%20into%20RMB%2C%20the%20main%20determinant%20of%20exporters'%20FX%20conversion%20is%20China's%20domestic%20demand%20and%20business%20confidence%2C%20which%20remain%20weak%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Hu%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20renminbi%2C%20the%20official%20name%20for%20the%20Chinese%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PBOC%20may%20not%20want%20to%20see%20a%20rapid%20CNY%20appreciation%20that%20hurts%20exports%2C%20the%20main%20bright%20spot%20for%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-chinese-yuan-cny-cnh-hits-high-aggressive-stimulus-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727242478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F56d481c5dd089536178b45e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fchina-economy-chinese-yuan-cny-cnh-hits-high-aggressive-stimulus-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20dollar%20to%20offshore%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%20or%20CNH%20rate%20fell%20to%20as%20low%20as%206.9951%2C%20the%20first%20time%20it%20breached%20the%207%20per%20dollar%20level%20since%20May%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fchina-economy-chinese-yuan-cny-cnh-hits-high-aggressive-stimulus-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyanka-Samantha%20light%20up%20%E2%80%98Citadel%E2