phic%20Institution%2C%20noted%20that%20while%20it's%20rare%2C%20plant%20life%20does%20respond%20quickly%20to%20heavy%20rain%20events%20in%20this%20part%20of%20Africa.%20When%20substantial%20rain%20falls%2C%20dunes%20transform%20into%20lush%2C%20green%20landscapes%20for%20a%20brief%20time%20as%20plants%20take%20full%20advantage%20of%20the%20moisture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAn%20extratropical%20cyclone%20over%20the%20Sahara%20Desert%20drenched%20parts%20of%20Morocco%20and%20Algeria%20%E2%80%93%20bringing%20up%20to%20a%20year's%20worth%20of%20rain%20to%20some%20areas.%20%F0%9F%8C%A7%EF%B8%8F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNASA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40nasa%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Terra%20satellite%20captured%20floodwaters%20and%20some%20Saharan%20lakes%2C%20usually%20dry%2C%20filled%20with%20water.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcuS1c73RoA%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcuS1c73RoA%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fm8Ga8G0FgO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fm8Ga8G0FgO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NASA%20Earth%20(%40NASAEarth)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNASAEarth%2Fstatus%2F1836071502384394313%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20Sahara%20was%20once%20covered%20in%20vegetation%20and%20lakes%20between%2011%2C000%20and%205%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20de%20Menocal's%20past%20research%20suggests.%20Now%2C%20even%20lakes%20that%20are%20typically%20dry%20are%20filling%20up%20due%20to%20this%20recent%20deluge%2C%20according%20to%20Moshe%20Armon%2C%20a%20lecturer%20at%20the%20Institute%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%2C%20Hebrew%20University%20of%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unusual%20rainfall%20event%20was%20triggered%20by%20the%20northward%20movement%20of%20the%20tropical%20rain%20belt%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Intertropical%20Convergence%20Zone%2C%20reaching%20farther%20north%20than%20usual%2C%20bringing%20heavy%20rains%20typical%20of%20equatorial%20regions%20into%20the%20Sahara.%20Some%20areas%20saw%20over%20half%20a%20foot%20of%20rain%2C%20which%20far%20exceeds%20the%20typical%20annual%20precipitation%20of%20just%20a%20few%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20rains%20largely%20affected%20sparsely%20populated%20areas%2C%20devastating%20floods%20have%20killed%20over%201%2C000%20people%20and%20affected%20around%204%20million%20across%2014%20African%20nations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Food%20Programme%20and%20the%20Associated%20Press.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20believe%20the%20shift%20in%20the%20rain%20belt%20is%20influenced%20by%20record-high%20ocean%20temperatures%20and%20climate%20change%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20further%20changes%20in%20rainfall%20patterns%20across%20Africa.%20However%2C%20as%20ocean%20temperatures%20balance%20out%20globally%2C%20the%20rain%20belt%20is%20expected%20to%20shift%20back%20south%2C%20potentially%20crossing%20the%20equator%2C%20according%20to%20de%20Menocal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727241300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fc2uglpr8_sahara-desert_625x300_25_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsahara-desert-turns-green-nasa-shares-stunning-image-of-transformation-6644222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Historically%2C%20the%20Sahara%20was%20once%20covered%20in%20vegetation%20and%20lakes%20between%2011%2C000%20and%205%2C000%20years%20ago%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsahara-desert-turns-green-nasa-shares-stunning-image-of-transformation-6644222%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20says%20'big%20threats%20on%20my%20life%20by%2