cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fipo-fundraise-thus-far-in-2024-third-highest-in-primary-market-history-124092500204_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fipo-fundraise-thus-far-in-2024-third-highest-in-primary-market-history-124092500204_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%2C%2038%2C%20Gets%20Life%20Term%20For%20Raping%20His%20Mother%2C%2060%2C%20In%20UP's%20Bulandhshahr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2038-year-old%20man%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20for%20raping%20his%2060-year-old%20mother%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Bulandshahr.%20The%20man%20raped%20his%20mother%20on%20January%2016%20last%20year%2C%20after%20which%20his%20brother%20reported%20him%20to%20the%20police.%20A%20fast-track%20court%20found%20him%20guilty%20and%20pronounced%20its%20judgment%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20rape%20case%20was%20registered%20about%20one-and-a-half%20years%20back.%20A%20woman%20accused%20her%20son%20of%20rape.%20Police%20had%20registered%20an%20FIR%20under%20relevant%20sections.%20The%20accused's%20brother%20was%20the%20complainant.%20A%20fast-track%20court%20has%20sentenced%20the%20convict%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20and%20fined%20him%20Rs%2051%2C000%2C%26quot%3B%20Bulandshahr%20rural%20police%20chief%20Rohit%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20counsel%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Sharma%20said%20he%20has%20never%20encountered%20a%20case%20like%20this%20in%20his%20career.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mother%20kept%20crying%20and%20repeated%2C%20'My%20son%20raped%20me'.%20The%20man%20took%20his%20mother%20to%20get%20fodder%20from%20the%20field%20and%20raped%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20said%20in%20her%20statement%20that%20her%20son%20took%20her%20to%20the%20field%2C%20gagged%20her%2C%20raped%20her%2C%20and%20pressured%20her%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20acts%20regularly.%20%26quot%3BI%20folded%20my%20hands%20and%20pleaded%20with%20him%2C%20but%20he%20raped%20me.%20I%20kept%20saying%20I%20was%20an%20old%20woman.%20I%20lost%20consciousness.%20When%20I%20regained%20it%2C%20he%20threatened%20to%20kill%20me%20if%20I%20told%20anyone%20about%20the%20incident.%20He%20also%20asked%20me%20to%20sleep%20with%20him%20every%20night.%20Somehow%20I%20came%20home%20and%20told%20my%20niece%20and%20son%20(the%20complainant)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20court%20order.%C2%A0The%20woman's%20husband%20died%2010%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20who%20examined%20the%20woman%20said%20that%20her%20body%20had%20no%20sign%20of%20external%20or%20internal%20injury.%20Citing%20a%20previous%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20noted%20that%20even%20if%20the%20doctor%20who%20examined%20the%20victim%20does%20not%20find%20signs%20of%20rape%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20ground%20to%20disbelieve%20the%20testimony%20of%20the%20complainant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20noted%20an%20earlier%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20victim%20of%20rape%20states%20on%20oath%20that%20she%20was%20forcibly%20subjected%20to%20sexual%20intercourse%2C%20her%20statement%20will%20normally%20be%20accepted%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20uncorroborated%2C%20unless%20the%20material%20on%20record%20requires%20drawing%20of%20an%20inference%20that%20there%20was%20consent%20or%20that%20the%20entire%20incident%20was%20improbable%20or%20imaginary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convict%20had%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20did%20not%20commit%20the%20crime%20and%20was%20innocent.%20The%20case%20against%20him%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20false%20and%20registered%20to%20usurp%20his%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court's%20order%20noted%20that%20the%20defence%20did%20not%20present%20any%20witnesses%20to%20prove%20a%20property%20dispute%20between%20the%20accused%20and%20his%20mother.%20%26quot%3BIt%2