%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECompletion%20of%20Full%20Line%3A%20Expected%20by%20March%202025%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETotal%20Stations%3A%2027%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOperational%20Hours%3A%206%3A30%20AM%20to%2010%3A30%20PM%20on%20weekdays%20and%20from%208%3A30%20AM%20to%2010%3A30%20PM%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrain%20Operations%3A%20There%20will%20be%20nine%20rakes%20in%20service%2C%20undertaking%2096%20trips%20each%20day.%20Each%20eight-car%20train%20is%20expected%20to%20carry%20around%202%2C500%20passengers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrain%20Captains%3A%2048%20train%20captains%20will%20operate%20the%20trains%2C%20which%20can%20technically%20run%20driverless.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20line%20will%20provide%20crucial%20connections%20for%20daily%20commuters%2C%20including%20access%20to%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20airports.%20Once%20fully%20operational%2C%20the%20Aqua%20Line%20will%20link%20southern%2C%20central%20and%20western%20parts%20of%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20areas%20along%20this%20line%20include%20Nariman%20Point%2C%20Mumbai%20Central%2C%20Worli%2C%20Dadar%20and%20a%20direct%20connection%20to%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai's%20Metro%20price%20structure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Aqua%20Line%2C%20the%20fare%20structure%20hasn't%20been%20officially%20confirmed%20yet.%20However%2C%20based%20on%20the%20fare%20structures%20of%20existing%20lines%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20follow%20a%20similar%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20an%20estimated%20fare%20structure%20for%20when%20it%20becomes%20operational%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E0-3%20km%3A%20Rs%2010%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E3-12%20km%3A%20Rs%2020%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E12-18%20km%3A%20Rs%2030%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E18%2B%20km%3A%20Rs%2040%20or%20more%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20passengers%20will%20receive%20paper%20tickets%20with%20a%20QR%20code%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20activate%20NCMC%20cards%20gradually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partial%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Metro%203%20corridor%20could%20have%20an%20immediate%20impact%20on%20travel%20within%20the%20city.%20The%20stations%20along%20this%20stretch%20connect%20vital%20locations%20like%20Santacruz%2C%20Marol%20and%20Ghatkopar.%20This%20underground%20line%20is%20expected%20to%20reduce%20road%20traffic%20congestion%2C%20especially%20in%20high-traffic%20areas%20such%20as%20the%20western%20suburbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20planned%20for%20completion%20in%202021%2C%20the%20Aqua%20Line%20faced%20delays%20due%20to%20various%20challenges%2C%20including%20environmental%20concerns%20over%20the%20Aarey%20car%20depot%20and%20slow%20construction%20progress%20by%20contractors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20Metro%20network%20is%20undergoing%20rapid%20expansion%2C%20with%20the%20Aqua%20Line%20being%20one%20of%2014%20planned%20metro%20lines%20designed%20to%20ease%20congestion%20and%20improve%20connectivity%20across%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20current%20and%20upcoming%20Metro%20Lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%201%20(Blue%20Line)%3A%20The%20first%20metro%20line%2C%20running%20between%20Versova%2C%20Andheri%20and%20Ghatkopar.%20It%20has%2012%20stations%20and%20covers%2011.4%20km.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%202A%20(Yellow%20Line)%3A%20This%20partially%20operational%20line%20connects%20Dahisar%20(East)%20to%20DN%20Nagar%20along%20the%20Link%20Road%2C%20covering%2018.6%20km%20with%2017%20stations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%202B%20(Yellow%20Line)%3A%20This%20extension%20of%20Line%202A%20will%20run%20from%20DN%20Nagar%20to%20Mandale.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%204%20(Green%20Line)%3A%20Running%20between%20Wadala%20and%20Kasarvadavali%2C%20covering%2032.32%20km%2C%20this%20line%20improves%20connectivity%20through%20central%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELine%205%20(Orange%20Line)%3A%20This%2024.95%20km%20line%20connects%20Thane