nd%20my%20home.%20My%20spirit%20came%20into%20my%20body%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20belonged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20gone%20to%20the%20Texas%20Renaissance%20Festival%20every%20year%20since%20I%20was%2016.%20Even%20when%20I%20was%20living%20in%20Australia%2C%20England%2C%20or%20Russia%20for%20work%2C%20I%20flew%20home%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20break%20my%20streak.%20I%20love%20the%20music%2C%20the%20animals%2C%20the%20craftsmanship%20%E2%80%94%20just%20everything.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20did%20the%20math%20I%20realized%20that%20someone%20was%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20running%20the%20Renaissance%20Festival.%20I%20realized%20I%20could%20create%20a%20business%20opportunity%20from%20my%20passion.%20In%20February%202010%2C%20I%20co-founded%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sherwoodforestfaire.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESherwood%20Forest%20Faire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20medieval%20Renaissance%20fair%20outside%20of%20Austin.%20I%20was%2040%20%E2%80%94%20right%20on%20schedule%20to%20start%20chasing%20my%20dreams.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1d54403-ae1a-45da-a91f-28e4d7e0ef38%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20went%20from%20business%20meetings%20to%20toasting%20at%20the%20faire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20the%20financial%20security%20to%20feel%20confident%20taking%20the%20risk%20of%20quitting%20my%20CEO%20job%20to%20start%20the%20faire.%20For%20two%20years%2C%20from%202012%20to%202014%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20building%20that%20business.%20I%20also%20learned%20more%20and%20more%20about%20combat%2C%20and%20started%20performing%20in%20sword%20fighting%20shows.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20day%20I%20was%20at%20the%20faire%2C%20literally%20on%20a%20horse%2C%20when%20an%20old%20friend%20called%20me%20about%20a%20venture%20he%20was%20starting.%20I%20told%20him%20I%20couldn't%20talk%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20playing%20dress-up%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20invited%20me%20to%20come%20see%20his%20technology.%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20it%20and%20started%20a%20software%20company%20with%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22George%20Appling%20in%20a%20pretend%20battle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f205b4d17aa3c7b2b54c3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221218%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20George%20Appling%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%202015%20to%202018%20I%20had%20a%20foot%20in%20both%20worlds%3A%20running%20the%20faire%20while%20also%20launching%20a%20tech%20company.%20I%20would%20travel%20to%20Barcelona%20for%20Mobile%20World%20Congress%2C%20a%20major%20tech%20networking%20event%20that%20was%20held%20annually%20in%20February%2C%20just%20before%20the%20faire's%20season.%20I'd%20be%20up%20till%202%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20then%20catch%20a%20flight%20home%20to%20Austin%20where%20I%20would%20open%20the%20faire%20with%20a%20midnight%20toast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20brutal%2C%20but%20I%20absolutely%20loved%20the%20work%20I%20was%20doing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8c90f21-579e-4144-831b-d3058d8174b7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%208%20businesses%20now%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20days%2C%20much%20of%20my%20time%20and%20attention%20goes%20to%20the%20Sherwood%20Forest%20Faire.%20We're%20open%20weekends%20in%20March%20and%20April%2C%20and%20run%20a%20summer%20camp%20during%20the%20summer%20where%20kids%20can%20have%20hands-on%20learning%20experiences%20with%20everything%20from%20blacksmithing%20to%20horse%20riding.%20I%20also%20co-own%20a%20mead%20business%2C%20sell%20historical%20weapons%20and%20armor%2C%20and%20rent%20castles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlus%2C%20I%20have%20pursuits%20not%20related%20to%20the%20middle%20ages%20%E2%80%94%20I%20do%20executiv