ical%20of%20third-party%20vendors).%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20dollar%20we%20save%20allows%20me%20to%20give%20you%20guys%20more%20stability%20and%20hire%20more%20people%20to%20make%20your%20life%20easier%2C%26quot%3B%20Donaldson%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIn%20every%20single%20freakin%20task%20assigned%20to%20you%2C%20always%20always%20always%20ask%20yourself%20first%20if%20you%20can%20find%20a%20consultant%20to%20help%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20dealing%20with%20people%20outside%20MrBeast's%20company%2C%20%26quot%3Bnever%20take%20a%20No%20at%20face%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBasically%20what%20I'm%20trying%20to%20convey%20is%20what%20we%20call%20'pushing%20thru%20no'.%20Don't%20just%20stop%20because%20one%20person%20told%20you%20no%2C%20stop%20when%20all%20conceivable%20options%20are%20exhausted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20more%20in%20the%20document%2C%20which%20we've%20published%20below%2C%20but%20these%20highlights%20capture%20some%20of%20the%20main%20themes%20that%20Donaldson%20repeatedly%20touches%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20employees%20are%20%26quot%3Bobsessive%2C%20learn%20from%20mistakes%2C%20coachable%2C%20intelligent%2C%20don't%20make%20excuses%2C%20believe%20in%20YouTube%2C%20see%20the%20value%20of%20this%20company%2C%20and%20are%20the%20best%20in%20the%20goddamn%20world%20at%20their%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c31470b3-2698-4203-9b45-4c8f5e038e13%5C%22%3EDid%20MrBeast%20practice%20what%20he%20preached%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20are%20these%20business%20principles%20actually%20put%20into%20practice%20among%20staffers%20who%20work%20at%20MrBeast's%20company%3F%20A%20fair%20amount%2C%20three%20former%20MrBeast%20employees%20told%20BI.%20They%20were%20granted%20anonymity%20because%20they%20weren't%20authorized%20to%20speak%20publicly%20about%20their%20time%20at%20the%20comp