n%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20Nations%20meeting%20in%20Laos%20a%20month%20earlier.%20Manalo%20said%20China%20made%20the%20situation%20%26quot%3Bvery%20dramatic%26quot%3B%20despite%20reassurances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20US%20said%20it%20had%20no%20plans%20to%20remove%20MRC%20from%20the%20Philippines%2C%20which%20also%20isn't%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20see%20it%20go.%20The%20move%20angered%20Beijing%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20made%20clear%20our%20opposition%20more%20than%20once%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Lin%20Jian%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxw%2Ffyrbt%2Flxjzh%2F202409%2Ft20240919_11493204.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20Thursday%20during%20a%20regular%20press%20conference.%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20deployment%20is%20a%20move%20to%20turn%20back%20the%20wheel%20of%20history.%20It%20gravely%20threatens%20regional%20countries'%20security%2C%20incites%20geopolitical%20confrontation%2C%20and%20has%20aroused%20high%20vigilance%20and%20concerns%20of%20countries%20in%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-china-missile-problem-getting-worse-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20military's%20Rocket%20Force%3C%2Fa%3E%20notably%20maintains%20a%20substantial%20missile%20arsenal%20that%20includes%20medium-%20and%20intermediate-range%20systems%20that%20put%20US%20assets%20and%20bases%20in%20the%20region%20at%20risk%2C%20leading%20the%20US%20to%20rethink%20its%20assets%20and%20capabilities%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20MRC%20woes%20may%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20the%20Philippines%2C%20which%20has%20expressed%20interest%20in%20acquiring%20its%20own%20mid-range%20weapons%20and%20training%20on%20the%20American%20weapon.%20Deploying%20the%20MRC%20in%20Japan%20is%20apparently%20on%20the%20table%2C%20too.%20At%20a%20Defense%20News%20conference%20on%20September%204%2C%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Army%20Christine%20Warmouth%20said%20the%20US%20and%20Japan%20had%20discussed%20placing%20a%20Typhon%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELin%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxw%2Ffyrbt%2Flxjzh%2F202409%2Ft20240918_11492497.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20press%20briefing%20last%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20US%20was%20%26quot%3Bhellbent%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20military%20investment%20in%20the%20Pacific%20region%2C%20noting%20that%20putting%20Typhon%20in%20Japan%20%26quot%3Bwill%20heighten%20arms%20race%2C%20exacerbate%20regional%20tensions%2C%20threaten%20peace%20and%20security%20in%20this%20region%2C%20and%20disrupt%20global%20strategic%20balance%20and%20stability.%26quot%3B%20Lin%20said%20that%20China%20has%20urged%20the%20US%20to%20abandon%20its%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222551%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tomahawk%20land%20attack%20missile%20in%20flight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669030e08893442a5155df3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223571%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArms%20control%20experts%20have%20expressed%20deep%20concern%20over%20an%20arms%20race%20after%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20INF%20Treaty.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%203rd%20Class%20Robert%20S.%20Price%2FReleased%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20in%20response%20to%20serious%20allegations%20of%20Russian%20violations%2C%20the%20US%20officially%20withdrew%20from%20the%201987%20Intermediate-Range%20Nuclear%20Forces%20Treaty%20%E2%80%94%20which%20banned%20nuclear%20and%20conventional%20ground-launched%20ballistic%20and%20cruise%20missiles%20with%20ranges%20between%20500%20and%205%2C500%20kilometers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20the%20door%20has%20been%20wide%20open%20for%20the%20development%20and%20deployment%20of%20these%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20allegations%20that%20Russia%20violated%20the%20treaty%20prompted%20Moscow%20to%20resign%20from%20the%20agreement.%20Russia%20is%20said%20to%20have%20violated%20the%20Cold%20War-era%20arms-control%20pact%20by%20developing%20and%20fielding%20the%20SSC-8%2F9M729%20missile%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArms-control%20experts%20have%20said%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20violation%20of%20the%20INF%20Treaty%20and%20subsequent%20US%20developments%20would%20likely%20have%20a%20snowball%20effect.%20Not%20only%20are%20new%20missiles%20showing%20up%20in%20the%20Pacific%2C%20but%20there%20are%20plans%20for%20Europe%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20some%20of%20its%20NATO%20allies%20formally%20announced%20in%20July%20they%20were%20pushing%20ahead%20with%20plans%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-europe-long-range-weapons-bring-back-cold-war-danger-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20develop%20and%20field%20new%20long-range%20strike%20options%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20seeing%20the%20value%20of%20such%20weapons%20in%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20Some%20experts%20suggested%20that%20this%20emerging%20arms%20race%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-allies-to-develop-long-range-missiles-fill-critical-gap-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20reflects%20one%20of%20the%20most%20dangerous%20aspects%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-new-us-missile-system-keeps-upsetting-china-mrc-typon-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727207698000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f2ed03cfb7f307e5746f0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-new-us-missile-system-keeps-upsetting-china-mrc-typon-2024-9%22