the%20health%20safety%20of%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDhabas%2C%20restaurants%20and%20food%20establishments%20should%20be%20thoroughly%20investigated%20and%20police%20verification%20of%20every%20employee%20should%20be%20done%20and%20necessary%20amendments%20should%20also%20be%20made%20in%20the%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Act%20to%20ensure%20the%20purity%20and%20sanctity%20of%20food%20items.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20now%20it%20will%20be%20mandatory%20to%20display%20the%20name%20and%20address%20of%20the%20operator%2C%20proprietor%2C%20manager%2C%20etc.%20at%20the%20food%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20chef%20or%20a%20waiter%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20wear%20masks%20and%20gloves%20and%20it%20will%20be%20mandatory%20to%20install%20CCTVs%20in%20hotels%2Frestaurants%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20incidents%20of%20adulteration%20of%20food%20items%20like%20juice%2C%20pulses%20and%20roti%20with%20human%20waste%20and%20dirty%20things%20have%20been%20seen%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20incidents%20are%20gruesome%20and%20have%20an%20adverse%20effect%20on%20the%20health%20of%20the%20common%20man.%20Such%20efforts%20cannot%20be%20accepted%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcrete%20arrangements%20are%20necessary%20to%20prevent%20such%20incidents%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20by%20running%20a%20statewide%20intensive%20campaign%2C%20verification%20of%20all%20the%20employees%20working%20at%20food%20establishments%2C%20including%20their%20operators%2C%20should%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20said%20this%20action%20should%20be%20completed%20quickly%20by%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Drug%20Administration%2C%20police%20and%20local%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20had%20ordered%20food%20stalls%20and%20fruit%20vendors%20along%20Kanwar%20Yatra%20routes%20to%20display%20the%20names%20of%20shop%20owners.%20The%20government%20argued%20the%20directive%2C%20which%20was%20criticised%20by%20a%20section%20of%20people%2C%20was%20aimed%20at%20promoting%20transparency%20and%20informed%20choice%20of%20kanwariyas%20regarding%20the%20food%20they%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Dayashankar%20Mishra%20'Dayalu'%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20(Independent%20Charge)%20for%20Ayush%2C%20Food%20Security%20and%20Drug%20Administration%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOrders%20have%20been%20issued%20that%20all%20the%20shops%20will%20be%20probed%2C%20CCTV%20cameras%20will%20be%20installed%2C%20employees%20of%20eateries%20have%20to%20wear%20mask%20and%20gloves.%20What%20is%20the%20benefit%20of%20hiding%20one's%20identity%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20opposition%20parties%20have%20criticised%20the%20government's%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavidas%20Mehrotra%2C%20SP%20MLA%20from%20Lucknow%20Central%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20the%20sale%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Dalit%2C%20backward%20and%20minority%20communities.%20Hence%2C%20this%20dictatorial%20step%20has%20been%20taken.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIn%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20SP%20had%20promised%20that%20it%20will%20come%20up%20with%20'samajwadi'%20canteens%2C%20where%20clean%20and%20adequate%20food%20could%20be%20purchased%20at%20Rs%2010%20per%20plate.%20If%20the%20intention%20of%20the%20CM%20is%20right%2C%20then%20shops%20and%20dhabas%20should%20be%20opened%20by%20the%20government%2C%20where%20a%20person%20could%20get%20a%20full%20meal%20for%20Rs%2010%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20Congress%20chief%20Ajay%20Rai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20GSTIN%20number%20in%20the%20nameplate%20of%20the%20hotel%2Featery%20o