A%20call%20for%20an%20audition%20led%20her%20to%20the%20role%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBittu%20ki%20mummy%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20%3Cem%3EGullak%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20series%20became%20an%20instant%20hit%2C%20with%20audiences%20praising%20Sunita%E2%80%99s%20impeccable%20portrayal%20of%20the%20nosy%2C%20hilarious%20neighbour.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20this%2C%20I%20used%20to%20do%20small%20roles%2C%20so%20when%20I%20found%20out%20about%20%3Cem%3EGullak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%E2%80%99s%20film%20career%20began%20with%20roles%20in%20%3Cem%3EEk%20Chalis%20Ki%20Last%20Local%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20later%20included%20critically%20acclaimed%20movies%20like%20%3Cem%3EStree%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EKedarnath%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EShubh%20Mangal%20Savdhan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20it%20was%20her%20breakthrough%20on%20OTT%20platforms%20that%20truly%20elevated%20her%20career%2C%20with%20her%20memorable%20performances%20in%20%3Cem%3EGullak%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20catapulting%20her%20to%20stardom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20journey%20reached%20new%20heights%20when%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F185859%2Fcannes-film-festival-meghalaya-india-dominic-sangma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalked%20the%20red%20carpet%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20representing%20her%20film%20%3Cem%3ESantosh%3C%2Fem%3E.%20For%20the%20small-town%20girl%20who%20once%20shared%20dingy%20rooms%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20it%20was%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Sunita%20inspires%20many%2C%20as%20her%20%3Cem%3Egullak%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20dreams%20has%20finally%20cracked%20open%2C%20with%20one%20dream%20materialising%20after%20another!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726836276000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hailing%20from%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Haldwani%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Sunita%20Rajwar%20was%20inspired%20by%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20cinema%20and%20took%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20to%20join%20the%20National%20School%20of%20Drama.%20She%E2%80%99s%20now%20known%20for%20her%20eminent%20roles%20in%20'Gullak'%2C%20'Panchayat'%2C%20and%20'Stree'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A89%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366893%2Ftruck-drivers-daughter-to-cannes-how-sunita-rajwar-brought-her-fathers-cinema-dreams-to-lifesunita-rajwar-inspiring-journey-panchayat-gullak-stree-kedarnath-movies-list-timeline-national-school-of-dra%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20Her%20Dad%3A%2022-YO%E2%80%99s%20Diabetes%20Insulin%20Carrier%20%E2%80%98Novocarry%E2%80%99%20Wins%20James%20Dyson%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInsulin%20vials%20necessitate%20storing%20at%202%20to%208%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20beyond%20which%20the%20drug%20loses%20efficacy.%20And%20naturally%2C%20this%20prompted%20Indians%20to%20come%20up%20with%20some%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98innovative%20hacks%E2%80%99%20in%20local%20parlance)%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20A%20few%20of%20them%20were%20Odisha%20native%20Komal%20Panda%E2%80%99s%20closest%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20a%20fourth-year%20student%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332593%2Fdesign-medical-devices-innovation-nid-harvard-student-save-lives-chennai-siddharth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20of%20Design%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Komal%20(22)%20recently%20made%20headlines%20when%20she%20was%20announced%20the%20national%20winner%20of%20the%20prestigious%20James%20Dyson%20Award%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplauding%20the%20ingenious%20tricks%20her%20friends%20devised%20to%20prolong%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20insulin%20while%20travelling%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20them%20stores%20the%20vial%20in%20a%20thermos%20flask%2C%20while%20the%20other%2C%20who%20lives%20down%20South%20and%20makes%2027-hour-long%20train%20trips%20back%20home%2C%20purchases%20a%20chilled%20bottle%20of%20water%20at%20every%20station%20in%20which%20she%20then%20places%20the%20vial.%E2%80%9D%20Think%20of%20it%20like%20a%20mini-fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClever%20as%20these%20innovations%20are%2C%20it%20baffled%20Komal%20how%20no%20one%20was%20finding%20the%20process%20cumbersome.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20had%20to%20be%20a%20simpler%20solution%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20caught%20herself%20thinking%20this%20during%20one%20%E2%80%98Technically%20Complex%20Project%E2%80%99%20lecture%20in%20her%20second%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FSPLrsJewqrA%3Fsi%3DPCV60HkUE2dY60Av%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Komal%2C%20this%20need%20to%20ideate%20stemmed%20from%20personal%20sentiment.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20watched%20my%20father%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266427%2Fmiracle-millets-diabetes-indian-food-recipes-weight-loss-woman-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggle%20with%20diabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20I%20was%20little.%20He%20would%20rush%20home%20every%20afternoon%20from%20his%20job%20in%20a%20steel%20factory%2C%20just%20so%20he%20could%20take%20his%20insulin%20shot.%20The%20factory%20does%20not%20have%20a%20refrigerator%20and%20ice%20packs%20prove%20impractical.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20Komal%20was%20unable%20to%20put%20her%20finger%20on%20a%20mental%20blueprint.%20But%20she%20was%20keen%20that%20the%20premise%20of%20the%20design%20be%20something%20people%20would%20%E2%80%98want%E2%80%99%20to%20use%3B%20something%20non-negotiable.%20%E2%80%9CLike%20how%20we%E2%80%99d%20never%20leave%20home%20without%20our%20earphones%20or%20power%20banks%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20user%20to%20form%20a%20companionship%20with%20Novocarry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENovocarry%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98portable%20cooling%20solution%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20apt%20to%20store%20medications%20like%20insulin%20that%20require%20refrigeration%20during%20transport.%20And%20it%20does%20this%20while%20proving%20to%20be%20discreet%2C%20convenient%2C%20and%20reliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENovocarry%3A%20A%20potential%20solution%20for%20diabetic%20patients%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20design%20student%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20serendipity%3B%20right%20from%20her%20foray%20into%20the%20bachelor%20in%20design%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F114959%2Fmigrant-workers-sleep-easy-design-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindustrial%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20NID%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20initially%20preparing%20for%20my%20law%20entrance%20exam%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20to%20winning%20the%20James%20Dyson%20Award%202024%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CNovocarry%20started%20out%20as%20a%20classroom%20project.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerceived%20as%20the%20gold%20standard%20for%20design%20awards%2C%20the%20James%20Dyson%20recognition%20fosters%20problem-solving%20attitudes%2C%20encouraging%20students%20to%20broaden%20their%20innovative%20minds.%20Recalling%20her%20introduction%20to%20the%20Dyson%20world%2C%20Komal%20recalls%20seeing%20the%20famous%20hairdryer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20fascinated%20with%20the%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%20Her%20excitement%20is%20still%20palpable