apping-Station-14-1726583256-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366328%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20Battery%20Smart%20Swap%20Station%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20Battery%20Smart%E2%80%99s%20swapping%20stations%20operate%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Pulkit%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20interoperable%20batteries%20for%20electric%20two%20and%20three-wheelers%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20easily%20locate%20the%20nearest%20swapping%20station%20via%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20app.%20Our%20goal%20at%20Battery%20Smart%20is%20to%20build%20a%20dense%20network%20of%20swap%20stations%20by%20ensuring%20EV%20users%20are%20within%20a%20one-kilometre%20radius%20of%20a%20station%20with%20zero%20wait%20time.%20At%20the%20station%2C%20EV%20users%20on%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20network%20can%20quickly%20exchange%20their%20depleted%20battery%20for%20a%20fully%20charged%20one%20in%20under%20two%20minutes%2C%20and%20conveniently%20pay%20for%20each%20battery%20swap%20directly%20through%20the%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20a%20battery-as-a-service%20model%2C%20we%20are%20making%20EV%20ownership%20more%20accessible%20and%20affordable.%20Our%20partner-led%20approach%20enables%20us%20to%20leverage%20existing%20infrastructure%20by%20partnering%20with%20small%20businesses%20and%20corner%20shops%20to%20rapidly%20expand%20our%20network%20and%20help%20boost%20their%20incomes.%20This%20has%20enabled%20us%20to%20expand%20our%20network%20to%20Tier%201%2C%202%2C%20and%203%20regions%20in%20India%2C%20where%20charging%20infrastructure%20is%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20their%20batteries%20are%20interoperable%2C%20Battery%20Smart%20claims%20to%20serve%20over%20200%20vehicle%20models%20with%20a%20single%20type%20of%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20new%20users%20have%20a%20smooth%20transition%20from%20their%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20(ICE)%20vehicles%20to%20EVs.%20Battery%20swapping%20allows%20them%20to%20mimic%20the%20refuelling%20experience%2C%20by%20replacing%20the%20depleted%20battery%20with%20a%20fully%20charged%20battery%20in%20under%20two%20minutes.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20adoption%20of%20electric%20mobility%20is%20simple%20and%20efficient%2C%20leading%20to%20greater%20savings%20in%20time%2C%20covering%20longer%20distances%2C%20and%20increasing%20incomes%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20swap%20would%20cost%20users%20between%20Rs%20100%20and%20Rs%20150%2C%20and%20it%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20over%2060%20km%2C%20claims%20Siddharth.%20EV%20users%20can%20also%20opt%20for%20various%20subscription%20plans%20that%20suit%20their%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20vehicles%20have%20smart%20meters%2C%20which%20indicate%20to%20the%20users%20when%20to%20swap%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20%E2%80%94%20from%20locating%20the%20nearest%20swap%20station%20to%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20done%20on%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20batteries%20they%20deploy%2C%20Pulkit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20we%20use%20are%20smart%20and%20interoperable%2C%20making%20them%20compatible%20with%20electric%20three%20and%20two-wheelers.%20These%20batteries%20are%20produced%20by%20different%20battery%20manufacturers%20but%20are%20identical%20in%20specifications%20and%20dimensions.%20This%20means%20that%20from%20a%20customer%E2%80%99s%20perspective%2C%20the%20same%20model%20of%20batteries%20is%20being%20swapped.%20We%20source%20our%20batteries%20fr