0battery.%20So%2C%20while%20they%20may%20be%20produced%20by%20different%20OEMs%20the%20specifications%20and%20dimensions%20will%20be%20uniform%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20swappable%20batteries%20are%20around%202%20to%202.5%20kWh%20in%20capacity%2C%20and%20weigh%20about%2012%20to%2015%20kg.%20The%20smaller%20batteries%20result%20in%20lower%20weight%20of%20the%20electric%20two-wheeler%20and%20yield%20better%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20greater%20range%20on%20the%20available%20charge.%20An%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333931%2Fbengaluru-startup-converts-petrol-two-wheeler-to-hybrid-electric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20two-wheeler%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20designed%20to%20run%20with%20one%20battery%2C%20whereas%20vehicles%2C%20such%20as%20e-rickshaws%20and%20e-autos%2C%20can%20be%20fitted%20with%20up%20to%20two%20such%20batteries%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20energy%20consumption%20and%20range%20requirements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20goes%20on%20to%20state%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20partner%20OEMs%20provide%20warranty%2C%20performance%20and%20safety%20on%20their%20products%2C%20and%20while%20we%20conduct%20quality%20testing%20on%20them%20before%20rolling%20it%20out%20into%20the%20market.%20We%20invest%20significantly%20in%20developing%20safe%20Battery%20Management%20Software%20(BMS)%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20effectively%20managing%20swappable%20batteries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-13-1726583416.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EV%20Battery%20Swapping%20Technology%20is%20the%20future%20of%20EV%20adoption%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%